# Production build — ADMIN app for https://adminvastaravaraya.spectranox.com
# Public/shared endpoints (login, settings, categories, image upload) + the images themselves
# live on the USER domain. The browser reaches them cross-origin (CORS is open).
VITE_API_BASE=https://vastaravaraya.spectranox.com/backend/api
# Admin CRUD API ships in THIS bundle (admin-backend/) on the same subdomain -> relative path.
VITE_ADMIN_API_BASE=/admin-backend/api
# Link back to the storefront.
VITE_SITE_URL=https://vastaravaraya.spectranox.com
